comment:
* An event emitted by a Preferences node to indicate that * a preference has been added, removed or has had its value changed.

* * Note, that although PreferenceChangeEvent inherits Serializable interface * from EventObject, it is not intended to be Serializable. Appropriate * serialization methods are implemented to throw NotSerializableException. * * @author Josh Bloch * @see Preferences * @see PreferenceChangeListener * @see NodeChangeEvent * @since 1.4 * @serial exclude

variables.name: key
variables.comment:
* Key of the preference that changed.
     *
     * @serial

variables.name: newValue
variables.comment:
* New value for preference, or <tt>null</tt> if it was removed.
     *
     * @serial

variables.name: serialVersionUID
variables.comment: searches for missing serialVersionUID fields are done.

methods.name: public Preferences getNode()
methods.comment:
* Returns the preference node that emitted the event.
     *
     * @return  The preference node that emitted the event.

methods.name: public String getKey()
methods.comment:
* Returns the key of the preference that was changed.
     *
     * @return  The key of the preference that was changed.

methods.name: public String getNewValue()
methods.comment:
* Returns the new value for the preference.
     *
     * @return  The new value for the preference, or <tt>null</tt> if the
     *          preference was removed.

methods.name: private void writeObject(java.io.ObjectOutputStream out) throws NotSerializableException
methods.comment:
* Throws NotSerializableException, since NodeChangeEvent objects
     * are not intended to be serializable.

methods.name: private void readObject(java.io.ObjectInputStream in) throws NotSerializableException
methods.comment:
* Throws NotSerializableException, since PreferenceChangeEvent objects
     * are not intended to be serializable.

methodNames: private void writeObject(java.io.ObjectOutputStream out) throws NotSerializableException
private void readObject(java.io.ObjectInputStream in) throws NotSerializableException
